.TH DESKTOP-EDITOR 1 "2026-02-15" "Daniel Nylander" "Desktop Editor Manual"
.SH NAME
desktop-editor - Visual editor for .desktop files
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B desktop-editor
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBdesktop-editor\fR is a GTK4/Adwaita application for visually editing .desktop files with preview, validation, and translation management. It supports editing Name, Comment, Exec, Icon, Categories and other fields, previewing how the app appears in launchers, managing translations per language, and validating against the freedesktop.org specification.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/desktop-editor/
Configuration files.
.TP
.I ~/.cache/desktop-editor/
Cached data.
